text: Aknazarovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Saryshevsky Selsoviet, Meleuzovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 168 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 34 km from Meleuz, 4 km from Saryshevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Meleuzovsky District
title: Aknazarovo
